text: Vanessa Erskine (born 12 July 1994) is an American wheelchair basketball player. She won a gold medal at the 2016 Summer Paralympics. She played for the University of Wisconsin-Whitewater. She played at the 2013 Youth Parapan American Games. == References == Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic gold medalists for the United States Category:American wheelchair basketball players
